*****************************************************************************
                        gst-nvdsmetautils
                             README
*****************************************************************************

===============================================================================
1. Prerequisites:
===============================================================================

Refer to the DeepStream SDK documentation for a description of the
"nvdsgst_metautils" plugins and API.

You must have the following development packages installed
   GStreamer-1.0
   GStreamer-1.0 Base Plugins

To install these packages, execute the following command:
   sudo apt-get install libgstreamer-plugins-base1.0-dev libgstreamer1.0-dev

===============================================================================
2. Purpose:
===============================================================================

This document shall describe about the gst-nvdsmetatils plugins.

It is meant for demonstration of how to use the gst-nvdsmetautils
elements namely nvdsmetainsert & nvdsmetaextract in the pipeline.

===============================================================================
3. To compile:
===============================================================================

  $ Set CUDA_VER in the MakeFile as per platform.
      For x86, CUDA_VER=11.6
  $ sudo make
